<div id="v490.2.2"><span class="G3778 s">(<i>And</i> this</span><span class="G582 s"> taxing</span><span class="G1096 s"> was</span><span class="G4413 s"> first</span><span class="G1096 s"> made</span><span class="G2958 s"> when Cyrenius</span><span class="G2230 s"> was governor</span><span class="G4947 s"> of Syria</span>.)</div>
