<div id="v490.2.6"><span class="G1161 s">And</span><span class="G1096 s"> so it was</span><span class="G1722 s">, that, while</span><span class="G846 s"> they</span><span class="G1511 s"> were</span><span class="G1563 s"> there</span><span class="G2250 s">, the days</span><span class="G4130 s"> were accomplished</span><span class="G846 s"> that she</span><span class="G5088 s"> should be delivered</span>.</div>
