<div id="v490.2.15"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G1096 s"> it came to pass</span><span class="G5613 s">, as</span><span class="G32 s"> the angels</span><span class="G565 s"> were gone away</span><span class="G575 s"> from</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G3772 s"> heaven</span><span class="G444 s"> G2532, the shepherds</span><span class="G2036 s"> G4166 said</span><span class="G240 s"> one</span><span class="G4314 s"> to</span><span class="G240 s"> another</span><span class="G1330 s">, Let us</span><span class="G1211 s"> now</span><span class="G1330 s"> go</span><span class="G2193 s"> even unto</span><span class="G965 s"> Bethlehem</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G1492 s"> see</span><span class="G5124 s"> this</span><span class="G4487 s"> thing</span><span class="G1096 s"> which is come to pass</span><span class="G3739 s">, which</span><span class="G2962 s"> G3588 the Lord</span><span class="G1107 s"> hath made known</span><span class="G2254 s"> unto us</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (the shepherds: Gr. the men the shepherds)</span></div>
<div id="v490.2.16"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G2064 s"> they came</span><span class="G4692 s"> with haste</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G429 s"> G5037 found</span><span class="G3137 s"> Mary</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G2501 s"> Joseph</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G1025 s"> the babe</span><span class="G2749 s"> lying</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G5336 s"> a manger</span>.</div>
