<div id="v490.2.38"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G3778 s"> she</span><span class="G2186 s"> G846 coming in</span><span class="G846 s"> that</span><span class="G5610 s"> instant</span><span class="G437 s"> gave thanks likewise</span><span class="G2962 s"> unto the Lord</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G2980 s"> spake</span><span class="G4012 s"> of</span><span class="G846 s"> him</span><span class="G3956 s"> to all</span><span class="G4327 s"> them that looked</span><span class="G3085 s"> for redemption</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G2419 s"> Jerusalem</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (Jerusalem: or, Israel)</span></div>
